NAME: Accumulated coverage ratio derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Accumulated coverage ratio from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET ACCMLTD_CVRG_RT =
        CASE
            WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 1 
                AND ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (14, 45,6, 8,73, 74) 
                THEN ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT/GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT

            WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 2 
                AND PRFRMNG_STTS=1 
                AND ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (4,41,47, 7,9) 
                THEN ACCMLTD_CHNGS_FV_CR/GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT
    
            WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 1 
                AND ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (77,76,9)
                THEN
                    CASE
                        WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS=26 THEN ACCMLTD_CVRG_RT = ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT/GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT
                        WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS=21 THEN ACCMLTD_CVRG_RT=GNRL_ALLWNCS_BNK_RSK+GNRL_ALLWNCS_CRDT_RSK/GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT
                    END

            WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR=2 
                AND PRFRMNG_STTS=1 
                AND IMPRMNT_STTS=0 
                THEN ACCMLTD_CHNGS_FV_CR/GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT
            
            ELSE NULL
        END;

NAME: Transfer between impairment stages derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Transfer between impairment stages from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET TRNSFR_IMPRMNT_STGS =
        CASE
            WHEN INTL_IMPRMNT_STTS = 23
                THEN
                    CASE
                        WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 24 THEN 3
                        WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 25 THEN 5
                    END

            WHEN INTL_IMPRMNT_STTS = 24
                THEN
                    CASE
                        WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 23 THEN 1
                        WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 25 THEN 6
                    END

            WHEN INTL_IMPRMNT_STTS = 25
                THEN
                    CASE
                        WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 23 THEN 2
                        WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 24 THEN 4
                    END
        END;

NAME: Accounting classification for short positions derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Accounting classification for short positions from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET SHRT_PSTN_ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN = 
      CASE
        WHEN SHRT_TRDNG_BK_SCRTY_PSTN_ACCNTNG_STNDRD = 4
        THEN 3
        WHEN SHRT_TRDNG_BK_SCRTY_PSTN_ACCNTNG_STNDRD = 3
        THEN 2
        ELSE 'N/A'
      END;

NAME: Time elapsed since initial recognition derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Time elapsed since initial recognition from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET TM_SNC_RCGNTN = DT_RFRNC - TKN_PSSSSN_DT,
        TM_SNC_INTL_RCGNTN = 
            CASE
                WHEN TM_SNC_RCGNTN/365 > 0 AND TM_SNC_RCGNTN/365 <= 1 THEN 20
                WHEN TM_SNC_RCGNTN/365 > 1 AND TM_SNC_RCGNTN/365 <= 2 THEN 27
                WHEN TM_SNC_RCGNTN/365 > 2 AND TM_SNC_RCGNTN/365 <= 5 THEN 29
                WHEN TM_SNC_RCGNTN/365 > 5 THEN 37
            END;

NAME: Accumulated write-off derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Accumulated write-off from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET ACCMLTD_TTL_WRTFFS = 
      CASE
        WHEN GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT = 0 AND CRRYNG_AMNT = 0 THEN ACCMLTD_WRTFFS
        ELSE N/A
      END;

    SET ACCMLTD_PRTL_WRTFFS = 
      CASE
        WHEN CRRYNG_AMNT <> 0 THEN ACCMLTD_WRTFFS
        ELSE N/A
      END;

NAME: Amounts derecognised for capital purposes derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Amounts derecognised for capital purposes from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET AMNT_DRCGNSD_CPTL_PRPS = 
      CASE
        WHEN SGNFCNT_RSK_TRNSFR_INDCTR = 1
        THEN CRRYNG_AMNT
        ELSE 'N/A'
      END;

NAME: Date/period of application of forbearance measure derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Date/period of application of forbearance measure from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET APPLCTN_FRBRNC_STTS_DT = 
      CASE
        WHEN DT_FRBRNC_STTS > DATEADD(month,-3,DT_RFRNC) 
        AND DT_FRBRNC_STTS < DT_RFRNC
        THEN 2
        ELSE -1
      END;

NAME: Allocated collateral value uncapped pre haircuts derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Allocated collateral value uncapped pre haircuts from its building blocks.

NAME: Commercial real estate loan indicator derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Commercial real estate loan indicator from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET CMMRCL_RL_ESTT_LN_INDCTR = 
      CASE
        WHEN TYP_CLLTRL = 10 OR PRPS = 13
        THEN 1
        ELSE 2
      END;

NAME: Current loan-to-value ratio derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Current loan-to-value ratio from its building blocks.

NAME: Accumulated negative changes derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Accumulated negative changes from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET ACCMLTD_CHNG_NGTV =
        CASE
            WHEN TYP_ABSTRCT_INSTRMNT_RL = 71
                AND TKN_PSSSSN_DT > DATEADD(month,-3,DT_RFRNC) 
                AND TKN_PSSSSN_DT < DT_RFRNC
                AND INTL_RCGNTN_VL - CRRYNG_AMNT < 0 
                    THEN INTL_RCGNTN_VL - CRRYNG_AMNT
            ELSE 'N/A'
        END;

NAME: Derived default status derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Derived default status from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET DFLT_STTS_DRVD = 
      CASE
        WHEN /*INSTRMNT.*/DFLT_STTS IN (18, 19, 20)
        OR /*PRTY.*/DFLT_STTS IN (18, 19, 20)
        THEN 6
        ELSE 14
      END;

NAME: Performing status derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Performing status from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET PRFRMNG_STTS = 
      CASE
        WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 1 
        OR FNNCL_ASST_INSTRMNT_TYP_CRR_123 = 28
        THEN 1
        ELSE 11
      END;

NAME: Gross carrying amount derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Gross carrying amount from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM: SET GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT = CASE WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (4, 41, 47, 7) THEN CASE WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 11 THEN FV WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 1 THEN FV + ACCMLTD_CHNGS_FV_CR END WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (6, 8, 9) THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN = 77 THEN CASE WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 26 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 211 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + GNRL_ALLWNCS_CRDT_RSK WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 212 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + GNRL_ALLWNCS_BNK_RSK END WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN = 9 THEN CASE WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 1 THEN CASE WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 26 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 211 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + GNRL_ALLWNCS_CRDT_RSK WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 212 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + GNRL_ALLWNCS_BNK_RSK END WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 2 THEN CASE WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 11 THEN FV WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 1 THEN FV + ACCMLTD_CHNGS_FV_CR END END WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (76, 73) THEN CRRYNG_AMNT WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN = 74 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (2, 3) THEN FV END;

NAME: Time past due band derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Time past due band from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM: SET TM_PST_DU = DT_PST_D - DT_RFRNC, TM_PST_DU_BND = CASE WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 <= 0 THEN 1002 WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 > 0 AND TM_PST_DU/365 <= 1/12 THEN 75 WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 > 1/12 AND TM_PST_DU/365 <= 3/12 THEN 9 WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 > 3/12 AND TM_PST_DU/365 <= 6/12 THEN 12 WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 > 6/12 AND TM_PST_DU/365 <= 1 THEN 16 WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 > 1 AND TM_PST_DU/365 <= 2 THEN 21 WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 > 2 AND TM_PST_DU/365 <= 5 THEN 29 WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 > 5 AND TM_PST_DU/365 <= 7 THEN 84 WHEN TM_PST_DU/365 > 7 THEN 85 END;
